Package: Movies.Recommender
Type: Package
Title: Movies Industy Data Analysis and Movies Recommendation Algorithms 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Junyu Leng <121090250@link.cuhk.edu.cn>, Puzhu Wang <121090555@link.cuhk.edu.cn>, Yiqu Yang <121090711@link.cuhk.edu.cn>
Maintainer: Puzhu Wang <121090555@link.cuhk.edu.cn>
Description: 
    Provide a framework for movie analysis, prediction and recommendation. The package contains three main parts.
    1. Based on the build-in movie dataset, you can get exploratory data analysis (EDA) and visualization(line charts, pie charts, wordclouds).
    2. Based on your input user's historical data, you can get 
        (1) movie prediction by various machine learning algorithms (linear regression, neural network, et al.)
        (2) movie recommendation by various recommandation algorithms (RANDOM, UBCF, IBCF, POPULAR, SVD)
        (3) most similar user recommendation by cosine similarity 
    3. Based on your input movie text, you can get emotion classifications and emotion trends analysis by natural language processing (NLP). 
